Package: BARBI
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference for Distinguishing True Signal from Reagent Contamination in Ultra-Low Biomass Metagenomics NGS Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pratheepa Jeganathan
Maintainer: Pratheepa Jeganathan <pjeganat@stanford.edu>
Description: BARBI provides a reproducible, automated process to remove contaminating DNA from metagenomic shotgun sequencing data in the setting of ultra low-biomass samples.
